title: Organic Farma Zdrowia - Targowa
description: A part of the Organic Farma Zdrowia chain, situated in the Wilenska Shopping Centre, on the 2nd floor, opposite Carrefour. Offers a selection of produce, organic food (cereal, grains, flour, soy products, jams, juices, pasta, cheese, ready meals etc.), as well as cosmetics and detergents. Meat is sold, too.
